'''非24小時睡眠覺醒障礙'''<ref>{{cite journal|journal=中華職業醫學雜誌|volume=22|issue=3|page=160|year=2015|title=輪班工作之健康效應：系統性回顧與統合分析|author1=王建楠|author2=李璧伊|url=https://bach.ccu.edu.tw/Site/nu20908/Document/file_Bf5tqZ.pdf|format=PDF}}</ref>（{{lang-en|Non-24-hour sleep–wake disorder}}，簡稱：{{lang|en|non-24}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.sleepreviewmag.com/2015/05/need-know-non-24/|title=What You Need to Know About Non-24|last=Fadden|first=James S. P.|website=Sleep Review|language=en-US|access-date=2019-06-26}}</ref>、{{lang|en|N24SWD}}<ref name=AASM2015>{{cite journal |last1=Auger |first1=RR |last2=Burgess |first2=HJ |last3=Emens |first3=JS |last4=Deriy |first4=LV |last5=Thomas |first5=SM |last6=Sharkey |first6=KM |title=Clinical Practice Guideline for the Treatment of Intrinsic Circadian Rhythm Sleep–Wake Disorders: Advanced Sleep–Wake Phase Disorder (ASWPD), Delayed Sleep–Wake Phase Disorder (DSWPD), Non-24-Hour Sleep–Wake Rhythm Disorder (N24SWD), and Irregular Sleep–Wake Rhythm Disorder (ISWRD). An Update for 2015: An American Academy of Sleep Medicine Clinical Practice Guideline. |journal=Journal of Clinical Sleep Medicine |date=2015-10-15 |volume=11 |issue=10 |pages=1199–236 |doi=10.5664/jcsm.5100 |pmid=26414986|pmc=4582061 }}</ref>），又稱'''非24小時睡眠周期綜合症'''、'''非24小時睡醒症候群'''<ref>{{cite book|title=专家解答失眠症|editor=赵忠新|isbn=7-5439-2828-0|page=107}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title=睡眠决定健康|author=伊济科夫斯基|isbn=978-7-80729-410-8|page=137}}</ref>，是一种[[睡眠障碍|睡眠障碍]]，患者的[[昼夜节律|昼夜节律]]和[[太阳日|太阳日]]脱节，多为每天推迟数十分钟，造成社会生活上的困难。该疾患最初在[[盲|全盲人]]身上发现，随后也在健视人中发现。

难以通过[[安眠药|安眠药]]治疗<ref>{{Cite book|author=山寺博史|editor=メラトニン研究会|script-title=ja:メラトニン研究の最近の進歩|publisher=星和書店|year=2004|isbn=978-4791105304|pages=179-180, 184}}</ref>。

